Hesitation Marks is the upcoming eighth studio album by American industrial rock act Nine Inch Nails, to be released on September 3, 2013. The album title is derived from hesitation wounds, wounds produced by testing a bladed weapon before attempting suicide or self-harming. The album will be available in two different masters for digital download, a "standard" version and an "Audiophile Mastered Version" 
- the latter having extended dynamic range, not meant to be competitive in the loudness war.
